org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl

Class MinimalDepthHardObjective

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl.BaseObjective
      • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl.MinimalDepthHardObjective
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IObjective

    public class MinimalDepthHardObjective
extends BaseObjective
    This hard objective is fulfilled if the trajectory is longer than a predefined number. A minimum length if 0 means all trajectory will be regarded as a solution.
